{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[F]A thorn was left in my heart by a [G7]rose
[C7]Of fragrance and beauty [F]divine
[G7]A thorn was left in my heart by a rose
[C7]A rose that I thought was all [F]mine
{end_of_verse}

